reviewText: Yes absolutely thank u for ur service

I finally got this movie. The movie is great, the DVD quality is great. After a bad experience with this movie before, I finally got a good copy. This seller even put the scene index so you can rewind and forward as you please. I had also been looking for this movie. I have it in VHS but the DVD is much better. As for the movie, it is one of Cantinflas' best, I watch it from time to time, and makes me laugh every time I see it. I definitely recommend this seller for old movies, meet the expectations.
